<Speech gate:gateId="80632" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="80459" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="80049" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΟΥΣΑ</Parlmember> (<SpeechStart gate:gateId="80340" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="80178" majorType="speaker">Μαρία Κόλλια-Τσαρουχά</Chairman>):</SpeechStart></SpeechStart> Τι «αφήστε την», κύριε Υπουργέ; Τι είμαστε εδώ;</Speech>
